  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <strong>Carro</strong>, the lone carrot or Brock the <strong>Broccoli</strong> on a mission to take back the Veg out World from all the moldy fruits and vegetables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A throw back to the old classics of how the FPS originated. Get in and get blasting with all the weapons you can handle and the enemies you can blast! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you can expect:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 different weapons, most with alternative fire modes too and more to come.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 9 single player stages filled with up to 5 levels per stage, keeping you entertained for endless amounts of time!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heap of different enemies per stage and building up to keep the entertainment and adrenaline pumping.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every stage has a different boss to keep you on your toes and wanting more at all times!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A survival mode per boss where enemies keep on spawning and things just get harder each second you wait!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heaps more too, a fun, jam packed, crazy game!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A crazy bad Orange boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/c03efeb67bb368bac35b97fce874331b.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/c03efeb67bb368bac35b97fce874331b.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/c03efeb67bb368bac35b97fce874331b.mp4?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some Tomato Blasting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/97941dcb5a6de4a2e84a996a998de534.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/97941dcb5a6de4a2e84a996a998de534.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/97941dcb5a6de4a2e84a996a998de534.mp4?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blueberry sniping!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/6ff2fbc10c55419f0dedbedf9cfd144f.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/6ff2fbc10c55419f0dedbedf9cfd144f.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/6ff2fbc10c55419f0dedbedf9cfd144f.mp4?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apple gun madness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/352b66542c9649fa84ae4fb7d9ed0def.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/352b66542c9649fa84ae4fb7d9ed0def.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/352b66542c9649fa84ae4fb7d9ed0def.mp4?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carrot bomb goes boom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/2baf7bca16b7706642f487e64a93babb.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/2baf7bca16b7706642f487e64a93babb.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/2baf7bca16b7706642f487e64a93babb.mp4?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? Get in there as <strong>Carro or Brock </strong>and do some damage and blast your way through the Veg out World. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, come join in on the discord and help shape our game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Happy Veg out Crew! :)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <strong>Carro</strong>, the lone carrot or Brock the <strong>Broccoli</strong> on a mission to take back the Veg out World from all the moldy fruits and vegetables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A throw back to the old classics of how the FPS originated. Get in and get blasting with all the weapons you can handle and the enemies you can blast! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you can expect:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 different weapons, most with alternative fire modes too and more to come.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 9 single player stages filled with up to 5 levels per stage, keeping you entertained for endless amounts of time!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heap of different enemies per stage and building up to keep the entertainment and adrenaline pumping.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every stage has a different boss to keep you on your toes and wanting more at all times!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A survival mode per boss where enemies keep on spawning and things just get harder each second you wait!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heaps more too, a fun, jam packed, crazy game!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A crazy bad Orange boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/c03efeb67bb368bac35b97fce874331b.poster.avif?t=1759441086\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extras/c03efeb67bb368bac35b97fce874331b.webm?t=1759441086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2085290/extr